#: ../../../install-nix.md:3
msgid "Install Nix"
msgstr "Nix 설치"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:4
msgid "Requirements:"
msgstr "요구사항:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:5
msgid ""
"Prior to installation, you might first need to install `xz-utils` or similar "
"for decompressing the Nix binary tarball (`.tar.xz`) that will be downloaded "
"via the scripts below."
msgstr ""
"설치에 앞서, 아래 스크립트를 통해 다운로드할 Nix 바이너리 tarball(`.tar.xz`)"
"의 압축을 해제하려면 `xz-utils` 또는 이와 유사한 도구를 먼저 설치해야 합니다."

#: ../../../install-nix.md:0
msgid "Linux"
msgstr "Linux"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:12 ../../../install-nix.md:24
msgid "Install Nix via the recommended [multi-user installation]:"
msgstr "권장 방식인 [다중 사용자(multi-user) 설치]를 통해 Nix를 설치합니다:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:14 ../../../install-nix.md:52
msgid "$ curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh -s -- --daemon\n"
msgstr "$ curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh -s -- --daemon\n"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:18
msgid ""
"On Arch Linux, you can alternatively [install Nix through `pacman`](https://"
"wiki.archlinux.org/title/Nix#Installation)."
msgstr ""
"Arch Linux의 경우, [`pacman`을 통해 Nix를 설치](https://wiki.archlinux.org/"
"title/Nix#Installation)할 수도 있습니다."

#: ../../../install-nix.md:0
msgid "macOS"
msgstr "macOS"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:26
msgid "$ curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh\n"
msgstr "$ curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh\n"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:31
msgid "**Updating to macOS 15 Sequoia**"
msgstr "**macOS 15 Sequoia 업데이트**"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:33
msgid "If you recently updated to macOS 15 Sequoia and are getting the error"
msgstr ""
"최근 macOS 15 Sequoia로 업데이트한 후 Nix 명령어를 실행할 때 다음 오류가 발생"
"한다면"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:34
msgid "error: the user '_nixbld1' in the group 'nixbld' does not exist\n"
msgstr "error: the user '_nixbld1' in the group 'nixbld' does not exist\n"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:37
msgid ""
"when running Nix commands, refer to GitHub issue [NixOS/nix#10892](https://"
"github.com/NixOS/nix/issues/10892) for instructions to fix your installation "
"without reinstalling."
msgstr ""
"Nix를 재설치하지 않고 문제를 해결하는 방법은 GitHub 이슈 [NixOS/nix#10892]"
"(https://github.com/NixOS/nix/issues/10892)를 참고하세요."

#: ../../../install-nix.md:0
msgid "Windows (WSL2)"
msgstr "Windows (WSL2)"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:44
msgid "Install Nix via the recommended [single-user installation]:"
msgstr "권장 방식인 [단일 사용자(single-user) 설치]를 통해 Nix를 설치합니다:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:46
msgid "$ curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh -s -- --no-daemon\n"
msgstr "$ curl -L https://nixos.org/nix/install | sh -s -- --no-daemon\n"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:50
msgid ""
"However, if you have [systemd support] enabled, install Nix via the "
"recommended [multi-user installation]:"
msgstr ""
"하지만 [systemd 지원]이 활성화되어 있다면, 권장 방식인 [다중 사용자(multi-"
"user) 설치]를 통해 Nix를 설치합니다:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:0
msgid "Docker"
msgstr "Docker"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:62
msgid "Start a Docker shell with Nix:"
msgstr "Nix가 포함된 Docker 쉘 시작:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:64
msgid "$ docker run -it nixos/nix\n"
msgstr "$ docker run -it nixos/nix\n"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:68
msgid "Or start a Docker shell with Nix exposing a `workdir` directory:"
msgstr "또는 `workdir` 디렉토리를 노출해 Nix가 포함된 Docker 쉘 시작:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:70
msgid ""
"$ mkdir workdir\n"
"$ docker run -it -v $(pwd)/workdir:/workdir nixos/nix\n"
msgstr ""
"$ mkdir workdir\n"
"$ docker run -it -v $(pwd)/workdir:/workdir nixos/nix\n"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:75
msgid ""
"The `workdir` example from above can also be used to start hacking on "
"Nixpkgs:"
msgstr ""
"위의 `workdir` 예제는 Nixpkgs 작업을 시작하는 데에도 사용할 수 있습니다:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:77
msgid ""
"$ git clone git@github.com:NixOS/nixpkgs\n"
"$ docker run -it -v $(pwd)/nixpkgs:/nixpkgs nixos/nix\n"
"bash-5.1# nix-build -I nixpkgs=/nixpkgs -A hello\n"
"bash-5.1# find ./result # this symlink points to the build package\n"
msgstr ""
"$ git clone git@github.com:NixOS/nixpkgs\n"
"$ docker run -it -v $(pwd)/nixpkgs:/nixpkgs nixos/nix\n"
"bash-5.1# nix-build -I nixpkgs=/nixpkgs -A hello\n"
"bash-5.1# find ./result # this symlink points to the build package\n"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:87
msgid "Verify installation"
msgstr "설치 확인"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:89
msgid "Check the installation by opening **a new terminal** and typing:"
msgstr "**새 터미널**을 열고 다음을 입력해 설치를 확인하세요:"

#: ../../../install-nix.md:91
msgid ""
"$ nix --version\n"
"nix (Nix) 2.11.0\n"
msgstr ""
"$ nix --version\n"
"nix (Nix) 2.11.0\n"
